<p> <crazy>atha ca <app><lem wit="#ceteri">tatkamalamadhye</lem><rdg wit="#U1">tatkamalaṃ</rdg></app> <app><lem wit="#ceteri">mukhaṃ</lem><rdg wit="#U1">adhomukhaṃ</rdg></app> tiṣṭhati/ asya kamalasya <app><lem wit="#ceteri">dhyānād ātmaprakāśo</lem><rdg wit="#B #P #L">dhyānākāśo</rdg><rdg wit="#U2">dhyānād ātprakāśo</rdg></app> <note type="philcomm" target="#right(328)">Since the evidence of the manuscript's lack of meaningfulness of this passage, I decided to emend according to the source text.</note><anchor xml:id="328"/>bhavati/</crazy> <note type="source" target="#right(328)">Ysv<hi rend="sup">PT</hi>: yathā sūryaprakāśena ūrddhvavaktraṃ prakāśitam | ātmadhyānāt sadā tatra āyur vṛddhir dine dine |</note><anchor xml:id="328"/><app><lem wit="#ceteri">prakāśād a</lem><rdg wit="#L">prakāśāvan</rdg></app><app><lem wit="#P #U1 #U2">naṃtaraṃ</lem><rdg wit="#B">anaṃtara |</rdg><rdg wit="#L">aṃtaraṃ</rdg></app> <app><lem wit="#ceteri">kamalam ū</lem><rdg wit="#B">kamalaṃ</rdg></app><app><lem wit="#ceteri">ūrdhvamukhaṃ</lem><rdg wit="#B">mūrdhvaṃ mukhaṃ</rdg></app> bhavati/ <app><lem wit="#ceteri">tathā</lem><rdg wit="#U1">yathā</rdg></app> <app><lem wit="#U2">sūryaprakāśād anaṃtaraṃ</lem><rdg wit="#B">sūryo prakāśānaṃtaraṃ |</rdg><rdg wit="#P #L #U1">sūryaprakāśānaṃtaraṃ</rdg></app> tadā <app><lem wit="#B #P #L">kamalamadhye</lem><rdg wit="#U2">malamadhye</rdg><rdg wit="#U1">kamalaṃ</rdg></app> <app><lem wit="#ceteri">vikasati</lem><rdg wit="#P">visati</rdg></app>/ <app><lem wit="#U2 #P">tathedam a</lem><rdg wit="#U1">tathā idam</rdg><rdg wit="#B #L">tam</rdg></app><app><lem wit="#U1">py ā</lem><rdg wit="#ceteri">api</rdg></app>tma<app><lem wit="#P #U2">prakāśānaṃtaram ū</lem><rdg wit="#U1">ātmaprakāśānataram</rdg></app><app><lem wit="#L #U1 #U2">rdhvamukhaṃ</lem><rdg wit="#P">ūrdhvaṃ mukhaṃ</rdg><rdg wit="#B">mūrdhvaṃ mukhaṃ</rdg></app> vikasati/ <app><lem wit="#ceteri">tanmadhye</lem><rdg wit="#U2">tanamadhye</rdg></app> paramānanda<app><lem wit="#ceteri">rūpābhūmir bha</lem><rdg wit="#L">°rūpo bhūmir</rdg></app><app><lem wit="#ceteri">vati</lem><rdg wit="#U1">bhavatī</rdg></app>/ tasyāhaṃso haṃsa iti saṃjñā// <app><lem wit="#P #U1 #U2">tasyā</lem><rdg wit="#B #L">tasya</rdg></app> madhye <app><lem wit="#ceteri">svātmano</lem><rdg wit="#U1">svātmanaḥ</rdg></app> <app><lem wit="#ceteri">dhyānād di</lem><rdg wit="#B #U2">dhyād</rdg></app>ine dine āyūr va<app><lem wit="#B #L">rdhayati</lem><rdg wit="#U1 #U2">varddhati</rdg><rdg wit="#P">varddhate</rdg></app>/ <note type="source" target="#right(329)">Ysv<hi rend="sup">PT</hi>: śaktiprasannatā syāc ca rogaśokavivarjitaḥ | yasya mudrābhyāsaśālī samyak siddhā ca khecarī |</note><anchor xml:id="329"/><note type="philcomm" target="#right(330)">Evidence of witness E resumes here.</note><anchor xml:id="330"/>rogā <app><lem wit="#ceteri">dūre</lem><rdg wit="#P">dūro</rdg><rdg wit="#L">dūrā</rdg></app> <app><lem wit="#ceteri">bhavanti</lem><rdg wit="#B">bhavati</rdg></app>/ <crazy><app><lem wit="#U2">tritayalokāṃtaḥ</lem><rdg wit="#P">tritayalokāṃta°</rdg><rdg wit="#E">tṛtīyalokāṃtaḥ</rdg><rdg wit="#B #L">tritayo lokāṃta°</rdg><rdg wit="#U1">trīvalī kṛtaṃ</rdg></app> samyak <app><lem wit="#ceteri">mudrā</lem><rdg wit="#E">samudrā</rdg></app> <app><lem wit="#P #L #U2">ca khecarī</lem><rdg wit="#B">ca khecari</rdg><rdg wit="#U1">bhavati khecarī</rdg><rdg wit="#E">khecarī</rdg></app>/</crazy> <note type="source" target="#right(331)">Ysv<hi rend="sup">PT</hi>: cidānandamayaṃ cittaṃ cetanā candrikānvitā | paramātmā mahāsūryaḥ sūrya ekaḥ prakāśakaḥ | prakāśānandayor aikyaṃ karttavyañ ca nirantaram | dīptas tathā mahājyotīr avirbhāti paraṃ padam |</note><anchor xml:id="331"/><app><lem wit="#P">cidānandādayaś ca</lem><rdg wit="#U2">cidānaṃdādayaḥ</rdg><rdg wit="#U1">cidānaṃdodayaṃś</rdg><rdg wit="#B #L">cidānaṃdādayoś</rdg><rdg wit="#E">cidānandādvayaś</rdg></app><app><lem resp="#ego" type="emendation">ndrikā</lem><rdg wit="#L">em. caṃḍrīkā°</rdg><rdg wit="#B">caḍrikā</rdg><rdg wit="#P">caḍriś cadrikā</rdg><rdg wit="#E">candracaṃdrikā</rdg><rdg wit="#U1">caṃdraḥś cetanāś</rdg><rdg wit="#U2">caṃdrāś cadrikā</rdg></app> <app><lem resp="#ego" type="emendation">cetanānvitā</lem><rdg wit="#E">em. veti nāmānvitaḥ</rdg><rdg wit="#P">cetanānvitāḥ</rdg><rdg wit="#B #L">cetanvitāḥ</rdg><rdg wit="#U1">caṃdrakānvitā</rdg><rdg wit="#U2">cetanānvitaḥ</rdg></app>/ <app><lem wit="#U1">paramātmāmahāsūryaraśmipuṃjaḥ</lem><rdg wit="#B #L #P #U2">paramātmāmahāsūryaraśmipuṃja°</rdg><rdg wit="#E">paramātmanāsaharaśmipuṃja°</rdg></app> <app><lem wit="#ceteri">prakāśakaḥ</lem><rdg wit="#E">prakāśaḥ</rdg></app>/ prakāśānaṃdayor aikyaṃ prakartavyaṃ/ niraṃtaraṃ svayam a<app><lem wit="#ceteri">gnir ma</lem><rdg wit="#E">manasi</rdg></app><app><lem wit="#ceteri">hājyotir ā</lem><rdg wit="#U1">mahājyotiś</rdg></app><app><lem wit="#ceteri">bhāti</lem><rdg wit="#U1">abhāti</rdg></app> <app><lem wit="#E #P #L #U1">paramaṃ padaṃ</lem><rdg wit="#B">paramapadam</rdg><rdg wit="#U2">paraṃmapadaṃ</rdg></app>/ <note type="source" target="#right(331)">Ysv<hi rend="sup">PT</hi>: sadoditaṃ manaḥsūryaṃ candrajyotir ivekṣate |</note><anchor xml:id="331"/><app><lem wit="#B #E #L">sadoditamanaś ca</lem><rdg wit="#U1">sadoditamanaḥś</rdg><rdg wit="#P #U2">sadoditaṃ manaś</rdg></app><app><lem wit="#ceteri">ndraḥ</lem><rdg wit="#B">cadraḥ</rdg></app> <app><lem wit="#E">sūryodayam i</lem><rdg wit="#B #P #L #U2">sūryodaya</rdg><rdg wit="#U1">sūryodaye</rdg></app><app><lem wit="#ceteri">vekṣate</lem><rdg wit="#E">avekṣate</rdg><rdg wit="#U1">ca lakṣyate</rdg></app> tena <app><lem wit="#ceteri">grasto</lem><rdg wit="#U1 #U2">graste</rdg></app> <app><lem wit="#ceteri">manaś ca</lem><rdg wit="#B">manaḥ |</rdg></app><app><lem wit="#ceteri">ndraḥ</lem><rdg wit="#B">ścaṃdraḥ</rdg></app> so 'pi <app><lem wit="#P">līnaḥ</lem><rdg wit="#B">lina</rdg><rdg wit="#L #U1">linaṃ</rdg><rdg wit="#E #U2">lipyaḥ</rdg></app> svayaṃ pade/ </p>
